Xag-ya are creatures of pure positive+energy resembling glowing white orbs with tentacles made out of the same white light as their bodies. They are inscrutible, alien things, and it is a matter of debate whether they are truly sentient.
Xag-ya are outsiders native to the Positive+Energy+Plane. Belonging to a class of creatures collectively known as energons, it attacks by utilizing positive+energy
to cause damage.Xag-ya hate Xeg-yi and attack them on sight. 

